sentences: Flo & Joan has been featured on BBC One's Live at The Apollo, the 2019's Royal Variety Performance and Richard Herring Leicester Square Theatre Podcast.
In 2018, they were featured in a Nationwide building society television advert.
They grew up in Portsmouth, lived in Toronto for a few years, and as of February 2019, now live in London.

They released an Amazon Prime Video special, Alive on Stage, based on their Edinburgh Fringe show in 2019.
Their song "Drank too much", which recounts a fictitious night drinking with a nonexistent friend Dino, has been featured on many comedy shows.
